{"tid":2449300,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個消失左既火星文用字","createTime":"2021-03-16T14:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T14:55:47.000Z","uid":39206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"435e7069024c7f86d64a1f000095c808daf88bc1","tid":2449300,"uid":39206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:24:13.000Z","msg":"Orz....<br />\n呢個火星文其實幾好用<br />\n<br />\n不過宜家應該好多人唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAF8TJ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAF8TJ7.jpg&h=7b79e343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n失意體前屈（最常見的型體為Orz），被歸為火星文的一種，是一種源自於日本的表情符號（又稱心情圖示），因型態上看似低著頭地跪倒在地上，用來表示「失意」、「挫折」、「悲憤」，甚至引申至「拜服」、「欽佩」等意思。"},{"pid":"1bd7d71d8be31244dc550ebff4c37b9581875688","tid":2449300,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:27:20.000Z","msg":"&gt;v&lt; 樓主巧叻豬 :3 啜卜卜"},{"pid":"d61830efe4f7b36c378851dabeeaf5502be3f819","tid":2449300,"uid":54995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:55:47.000Z","msg":"OGC"}]}